description: >
  A cabinet for strength, mobility, and conditioning. The Strength Console
  tracks your top sets per movement, current cycle, weekly volume, and
  recovery. Coach plans the week's training, suggests deloads when volume
  spikes, and keeps the program coherent across cycles. One agent: Coach.
